ActAppropriation Act No. 1, 2010-11
PrecisAppointment of STEWART BECK as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Federal Democratic Republic of Nepal, with residence in New Delhi; PERRY CALDERWOOD as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Guinea-Bissau, and as High Commissioner for Canada to the Republic of the Gambia, with residence in Dakar; DAVID COLLINS as High Commissioner for Canada to the Republic of Rwanda, with residence in Nairobi; and ALAIN LATULIPPE as High Commissioner for Canada to the Republic of Malawi, with residence in Maputo.
